{"tid":1982322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"”中聯辦睜大眼睛說，“你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白……”","createTime":"2020-04-21T06:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T05:02:24.000Z","uid":105976,"like":147,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"035119a7ffcb5cfaecc91ed119f8f7b3229bc48d","tid":1982322,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:51:06.000Z","msg":"中聯辦一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，&ldquo;中聯辦，你臉上又添上新傷疤了！<br />\n<br />\n&rdquo;他不回答，對柜里說，&ldquo;溫兩碗酒，要一碟茴香豆。&rdquo;便排出九文大錢。<br />\n<br />\n他們又故意的高聲嚷道，&ldquo;你一定又干預人家的內政了！<br />\n&rdquo;中聯辦睜大眼睛說，&ldquo;你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;什麼清白？我前天親眼見你公告指指點點的。&rdquo;<br />\n中聯辦便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，&ldquo;中聯辦不能算中央機構干預&hellip;&hellip;監督！&hellip;&hellip;中央監督，能算干預？&rdquo;<br />\n接連便是難懂的話，什麼&ldquo;新華社香港分部&rdquo;，什麼&ldquo;曲解&rdquo;之類，引得眾人都哄笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解佢地覺得會有人信  <br />\n理得你監督定乜撚<br />\n影響左咪干預囉  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f25d2a3c8310d1190e4ed3c052488a80cebfa4","tid":1982322,"uid":253992,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:54:18.000Z","msg":"魯迅真心勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />萬能Key嚟"},{"pid":"c6deaf5375dce85fcec29849892b7e00d6b228b8","tid":1982322,"uid":111316,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:54:38.000Z","msg":"孔乙己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1fec43b2304a79bbf5e2c52216bdab8f4b159c","tid":1982322,"uid":141419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:01:22.000Z","msg":"我邊有強姦人阿，我都冇射係入面"},{"pid":"7c5126e86172b6407905751e95c89ffa079ba373","tid":1982322,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"035119a7ffcb5cfaecc91ed119f8f7b3229bc48d","tid":1982322,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:51:06.000Z","msg":"中聯辦一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，&ldquo;中聯辦，你臉上又添上新傷疤了！<br />\n<br />\n&rdquo;他不回答，對柜